org.texgen.textures.complex
Class NoisyTexture

java.lang.Object
  org.texgen.textures.AbstractTexture
      org.texgen.textures.complex.NoisyTexture
All Implemented Interfaces:
Texture
public class NoisyTexture
extends AbstractTexture

A Noisy texture that takes an input source and sets the alpha channel based on noise(u,v)*size; This only creates a texture with noisy transparency. To mix with another texture see dirty.

Author:
Andy Gibson

Parameters:

speed - The rate of change of the noise over the texture (default 10)
octaves - Number of octaves to use to calculate the texture (default 10)
size - The size of the noise determines how much it affects the texture (default 0.5)
